Hi Lilly,

The discount is $4, i.e., $16 - $12.  So what you want to know is:

  $4 is what percent of $16? 

If you're not sure how to answer that, take a look at 

  Finding a Percentage
  http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/58173.html

and write back if it's not clear, or if you still have questions. 

Does this help?

- Doctor Ian, The Math Forum
